{"tid":753288,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[Tokyo Hot] 有圖有link","createTime":"2018-07-23T12:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T01:06:33.000Z","uid":3146,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b119653eb158781ed2b19c71e283aa156025be","tid":753288,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180723&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58474572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180723%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58474572&d=%2F0EGIoxpRdesLcAvUFiQ1mMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=65673a75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180723%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58474572&h=3aa56520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180723&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58474572</a><br />\n【熱浪●解構】東京都40.8&deg;C破觀測史上最高溫 兩股高氣壓「如蓋兩張毛毯」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱浪侵襲日本，東京都今午氣溫破1896年觀測以來最高紀錄，達40.8&deg;C，而東京北面的埼玉縣熊谷巿更錄得破全日本紀錄的41.1&deg;C。持續酷熱已令多人熱死，本月上旬更有逾萬人送院。當局周一再發出熱浪警告，呼籲民眾提防中暑。氣象專家指，目前日本受到兩股高氣壓影響，「像蓋了兩張毛毯」，令氣溫較過往酷熱。<br />\n<br />\n《朝日新聞》與《讀賣新聞》報道，東京都今天破觀測史紀錄，首度觀測到逾40&deg;C。青梅市先在日本當地時間中午12時49分，觀測到40.3&deg;C，後來又在下午1時29分，觀測到40.8&deg;C。而附近的埼玉縣熊谷巿也錄得破紀錄的41.1&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n日本今天有多個城市觀測到超過攝氏40&deg;C，日本放送協會（NHK）報導，岐阜縣多治見市今天中午觀測到40.5&deg;C高溫，甚至在東京都青梅市都出現40.8&deg;C。關東甲信地區是繼5年前在甲府市觀測到40.6&deg;C後，再度出現逾40度高溫<br />\n<br />\n至於關東和東海內陸地區，溫度亦持續高企，最高達40&deg;C。愛知縣和名古屋市也錄得39.5&deg;C，是歷來7月的最高溫度。<br />\n<br />\n根據官方數字，單是7月上旬，就共有1.2萬人因炎熱天氣而要送院，超過24人死亡，最年幼的死者是1名6歲男童。<br />\n<br />\n日本氣象廳解釋，目前有雙重高壓帶正在籠罩日本。在日本上空5,000米，有太平洋高壓，而上空約1.5萬米附近，則有從7月10日起覆蓋日本的西藏高壓。兩個高壓帶就像兩張毯子一樣，將暖空氣壓縮到位於中間的日本，令當地持續高溫。氣象廳估計，極端炎熱天氣將會持續至8月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/205203_e49e1a729ff88273815d168e061b6166.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F205203_e49e1a729ff88273815d168e061b6166.png&h=de4fd451&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e8eba7fcef55fe679710427f1553cf59418bd57","tid":753288,"uid":87741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"圖文相符<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b45974b52e77afa231a5de6c28ee99dc411885b","tid":753288,"uid":3146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79513d48a4129f1b4aa11b831de5985f3f1f5bf","tid":753288,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"你老母都好hot"},{"pid":"7757a27d1ba467e76550ef50284a53eb101c46eb","tid":753288,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427c628c265fd1ffb935f84d6f191b85f5ae23f6","tid":753288,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}